    "SDoH are notoriously under-documented in existing EHR structured data [10] [11] [12] 39.",
    "Our findings that text-extracted SDoH information was better able to identify patients with adverse SDoH than relevant billing codes are in agreement with prior work showing under-utilization of Z-codes 10, 11.",
